{
  "name": "SparklineGroups",
  "summary": "<p><strong>SparklineGroups</strong> 对象可包含多个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparklineGroup/SparklineGroup .htm#SparklineGroup.SparklineGroup\">SparklineGroup</a></strong> 对象。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.SparklineGroups\">SparklineGroups</a></strong> 属性可从现有 <strong>SparklineGroups</strong> 集合的父区域中返回该集合。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparklineGroups/SparklineGroups .htm#SparklineGroups.Add\">Add</a></strong> 方法可创建一组新迷你图。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparklineGroups/SparklineGroups .htm#SparklineGroups.Group\">Group</a></strong> 方法可创建一组现有迷你图。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例选择区域 A1:A4 并组合该区域中的迷你图，然后将该区域中第一个迷你图组的正数据点设置为可见，并将其颜色设置为红色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Group</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>))\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Points</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Markers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Points</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Markers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例取消组合活动工作表上区域 A1:A4 上迷你图组，并删除 A1 单元格中迷你图组。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroups = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>\n    sparklineGroups.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Ungroup</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ClearGroups</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表迷你图组的集合。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回关联的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象中的迷你图组的计数。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示单元格区域 A1:A4 上迷你图组的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Add",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>创建一个新的迷你图组并返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparklineGroup/SparklineGroup .htm#SparklineGroup.SparklineGroup\">SparklineGroup</a></strong> 对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例向区域 A1:A4 中添加一个迷你图组。该组中的迷你图为列迷你图并且绑定到区域 B1:E4 中的数据。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSparkColumn, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1!B1:E4&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例向活动工作表上区域 A1:A2 中添加一个迷你图组，并显示该工作表上单元格 A1 中迷你图组的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSparkLine, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:D2&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Type",
          "type": "XlSparkType",
          "description": "<p>迷你图的类型。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
