      "description": "<p>清除选定的迷你图组。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例清除活动单元格上迷你图组。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveCell</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ClearGroups</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例清除活动工作表上单元格 H1 中迷你图组，并显示该区域上迷你图组的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroups = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;H1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>\n    sparklineGroups.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ClearGroups</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sparklineGroups.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
